<bibRefCitation author="Krivokhatsky, V. A." editor="Noskov, G. A." journalOrPublisher="Mir i Sem'ya, St. Petersburg" pageId="0" pageNumber="22175" title="Red Data Book of Nature of the Leningrad Region. Animals" year="2002">Krivokhatsky and Kuznetsov 2002</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
